
maanā ki rañg rañg tirā pairahan bhī hai 
par is meñ kuchh karishma-e-aks-e-badan bhī hai 
aql-e-ma.āsh o hikmat-e-duniyā ke bāvajūd 
ham ko aziiz ishq kā dīvāna-pan bhī hai 
mutrib bhī tū nadīm bhī tū sāqiyā bhī tū 
tū jān-e-anjuman hī nahīñ anjuman bhī hai 
baazū chhuā jo tū ne to us din khulā ye raaz 
tū sirf rañg-o-bū hī nahīñ hai badan bhī hai 
ye daur kis tarah se kaTegā pahāḌ sā 
yaaro batāo ham meñ koī kohkan bhī hai 